= mechanical_github

This gem provides a automated API for working with github.

== USAGE
mg = MechanicalGitHub.new(username, password)
	Will return a logged in object, which you can use to interact with GitHub. 
	If you're using this often, you'll probably want to cache it.
	
mg.create_repository(name, description, homepage)
	Will create a new repository for the logged in session.
